{"product_id":"white-musk-attar-roll-on-6ml-al-saalim-perfumers-alcohol-free","title":"White Musk Attar (Roll-On 6ml) | Al-Saalim Perfumers | Alcohol-Free","description":"\u003cp\u003eExperience the soft, clean, and long-lasting fragrance of White Musk Attar by Al-Saalim Perfumers.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis attar is perfect for those who prefer a light, fresh, and elegant scent.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWhite Musk has a soothing aroma, making it ideal for everyday use.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWhether you are at the office, offering prayers, going out casually, or enjoying special moments, this fragrance fits every occasion effortlessly.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eKey Features\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eFragrance Type: White Musk\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eQuantity: 6 ml Roll-On\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAlcohol-Free\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eLong-lasting and skin-friendly\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eEasy-to-carry roll-on bottle\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSuitable for both men and women\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWhy You’ll Love It\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSoft and classy fragrance\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eGentle, headache-free scent\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePerfect for daily wear\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePremium packaging with an elegant bottle\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHow to Use\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eApply a small amount on your neck, wrists, or pulse points and enjoy a fresh, calming fragrance throughout the day.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"AL-SAALIM PERFUMES","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50471777370359,"sku":null,"price":179.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0923\/0755\/4551\/files\/7008594B-9D38-45B6-8453-FD87AC4A6428.png?v=1777869913","url":"https:\/\/alsaalimperfume.shop\/products\/white-musk-attar-roll-on-6ml-al-saalim-perfumers-alcohol-free","provider":"AL-SAALIM PERFUMES","version":"1.0","type":"link"}